videos.description: Saniya Chong with the ball, she drives to the basket and sinks the shot plus the foul.
videos.headline: Saniya Chong hits the and-one shot on a drive to the basket

videos.description: Q1 (0:05) CONN Crystal Dangerfield made Jumper.
videos.headline: Maryland head coach Brenda Frese annoyed about the last play of the 1st Quarter

videos.headline: Maryland gets a block then scores on the other end

videos.description: Kia Nurse gets the ball and hits the 3-point shot plus the foul.
videos.headline: Kia Nurse completes a 4-point play off an inbounds pass

videos.description: Q2 (0:02) MD Blair Watson made Layup.
videos.headline: Maryland gets a steal and a lay-up to cut into the UConn lead late heading into halftime

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson gets fouled hard while shooting the 3-pointer.  She then sinks the free throw to complete the 4-point play.
videos.headline: Katie Lou Samuelson takes a hard foul but still sinks the shot

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson sinks the jumper and draws the foul to extend Connecticut's lead over Maryland.
videos.headline: Katie Lou Samuelson makes another and-one jump shot

videos.headline: Brionna Jones lay-up cuts the UConn lead to 6

videos.headline: Destiny Slocum hits a deep 3-Point shot

videos.description: Kia Nurse gets the ball and passes to Saniya Chong, who hits the 3-pointer for Connecticut.
videos.headline: Saniya Chong makes a 3-pointer to extend Connecticut's lead
Saniya Chong gets a last second block on Maryland 3-Point attempt

videos.description: Connecticut coach Geno Auriemma talks about his team's play in the second half and his thoughts on their season to this point.
videos.headline: Auriemma: 'This was a heck of a win tonight'

videos.description: Dave O'Brien and Doris Burke break down Connecticut's 87-81 victory over Maryland.
videos.headline: Samuelson comes up big for Connecticut
